                Andreas Agopov, managing director of Ruslania Books Oy<br><br>
                <img src="pic1/Foto_Andreas7x9.jpg" width="229" height="208" alt="">
            </div>
            
            <br><br>
            Thus, as the company director, I express my thanks for the years past and my hopes for the years to come. We will not rest on our laurels: many more things need to be done to develop the business, meet the customer demand and enhance customer response. So do not hesitate to tell us about your wishes and ideas; we will do our utmost to fulfill them. Some of our customers have told me that they start their day by checking at <a href="http://www.ruslania.com">www.ruslania.com</a>, what new items have come out. I assure you that I will do my best to renew our site and selection fast enough for these clients to meet their expectations. We wish to be your favorite Russian-language book store!
            
            <br><br>
