            <td class="maintxt" width="100%" valign="top" style="padding: 10px;">
            <div style="font-size: 130%; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px">
            Ruslania Books Corp. - for everyone interested in Russia and Russian culture
            </div>

            Ruslania is a Finnish bookstore and publisher located in the center of Helsinki, Finland. We specialize in Russian products such as books, periodicals, newspapers, video-films, music, software and sheet music. We send our products all over the world. Ruslania offers a sumptuous choice of Russian encyclopaedical and fine literature. If you are interested in history or culture, leisure or learning Russian, you will find the best and the newest releases in the genre in Ruslania.
            
            <br><br>
            Many Finnish firms operating in the Russian market use our professional help in their purchasing of dictionaries and other books. Besides dictionaries we offer Russian business contact catalogues, encyclopedias etc. We also represent the most well-known Russian sheet music publishers. In our selection you will find sheet music from beginners' classes to the conservatoire level at a very low price. Ruslania imports only absolutely legal video-films and music. Thanks to this we can guarantee the best available quality. 
            
            <br><br>
            As a client of Ruslania you can forget about delivery delays and slow shipping. Thanks to our excellent supplier contacts and the geographical location next to Russia we are able to find and deliver the client's order quickly and very reasonable priced. Ruslania Books keeps a keen eye on the trends in Russian literature and is ready to deliver the newest books and the most recent information to everyone who is interested in the development in Russia.
            
            <br><br>
            We warmly welcome you in Ruslania. The bookstore is located in centre of Helsinki, at Lapinlahdenkatu 1 C and the opening hours are Monday-Friday 9 a.m. to 6 p.m. and Saturday 10 a.m. to 4 p.m.  
            <br><br>
            Where does the word Ruslania come from? Ruslan is a term that in a specific way gathers Russian culture and history. That is why we have chosen this name to represent our company. In Ruslania you will find much of the best things in Russian culture and literature. Our selection consists of books about Russian culture, history and politics; professional and scientific literature on different fields of knowledge, such as commerce, law, engineering; fiction (ranging from belles lettres to detectives), children's books, books on leisure activities etc. 
            
            <br><br>
            Our collection of books on Russian history, language and literature will be of interest to anyone who takes an interest in these topics. Many teachers and students of Russian are amazed at the sight of such a wide range of books for those who study or teach the language. Translators and interpreters find dictionaries (both the conventional paper editions and new electronic ones) useful for them in their work. Russian classics and contemporary literature are available in our bookstore. We also keep in stock translations of novels into Russian. Material needed in communication, such as Yellow pages of the Internet, reference books on CD-ROM and telephone directories of various Russian cities, reference book "Business-contact", maps and atlases are also available.
            </td>
